{"tid":753458,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"資深大律師胡漢清：民族黨開銀行戶口屬實際港獨行為","createTime":"2018-07-23T15:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T16:08:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2166f9dd45a81c306e9e15e2b02bee75d195288a","tid":753458,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:20:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1408448-20180723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1408448-20180723.htm&d=ZRRphKpkSfPSlxEcrJivEDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=fe490263\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1408448-20180723.htm&h=9430bc2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1408448-20180723.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n保安局計劃以《社團條例》取締主張港獨的香港民族黨，基本法研究中心主席胡漢清表示，去年中央和港澳辦清楚說明，宣揚港獨是分裂國家和危害國家安全，而民族黨並非只是談論港獨，而是曾嘗試申請成立公司和開銀行戶口等，這些都屬於實際行為。<br />\n<br />\n本身是資深大律師的胡漢清在本台節目說，學術討論港獨並不違法，但鼓吹、煽動年輕人參與港獨，即使形式是非暴力，都是違法違憲，要視乎普通法量刑負上法律後果，他舉例指，民政事務局前局長曾德成在「六七暴動」期間只是派發反殖傳單，就被判監2年。<br />\n<br />\n胡漢清相信，法庭獨立運作並解釋法律，會做好🇨🇳🇨🇳把關🇨🇳🇨🇳工作，被問到是否需要人大釋法處理有關問題，他相信本港法院足以處理案件。"},{"pid":"ed614a2ee13d2d973e46e9a5d8ea1e4301f0d78d","tid":753458,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:27:35.000Z","msg":"不如話屙屎都係港獨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca65a13cc12dc2fa6d443f592f597363fc9975e9","tid":753458,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ed614a2ee13d2d973e46e9a5d8ea1e4301f0d78d","tid":753458,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:27:35.000Z","msg":"不如話屙屎都係港獨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T15:29:27.000Z","msg":"屙屎當作生化襲擊"},{"pid":"e3623fffff7ad335cea2d503e15ec462bccb6817","tid":753458,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed614a2ee13d2d973e46e9a